trickery refer either to practices designed to mislead or to the qualities that
produce those practices. Deceit is the quality that prompts intentional
concealment or perversion of truth for the purpose of misleading: honest and
without deceit. The quality of guile leads to craftiness in the use of deceit:
using guile and trickery to attain one's ends. Hypocrisy is the pretense of
